NA for food as we only ordered 1 n its outsourced.very expensive.

Drinks wise n environment, all good.
Great place for a chill n catch-up session.
Services good and friendly. Able to play games and great place to have friends gathering over food and drinks.

Awesome selection of whiskey.

Happy hour until 8pm. All drinks need to be served by 8pm though.

No food menu.
Very nice ambiance; reasonable prices. Friendly staff and good choice of drinks
If you are looking for a drink in a really cool pub, this is it. Environment and music are great, staffs are extremely friendly
